graph TD
    A[Start] --> B[Initialize ShoonyaApiPy]
    B --> C[Login to API]
    C --> D[Define Global Variables]
    D --> E[Define Event Handlers]
    E --> F[Define Async Functions]
    F --> G[Main Function]
    
    G --> H[Create Tasks]
    H --> I[Connect and Subscribe]
    H --> J[Resample Ticks]
    H --> K[Trading Logic]
    H --> L[Update ATM Symbols]
    
    I --> M[WebSocket Connection]
    M --> N{New Tick Data?}
    N -->|Yes| O[Process Tick Data]
    O --> P[Update feedJson]
    P --> N
    N -->|No| M
    
    J --> Q[Resample Ticks]
    Q --> R[Calculate Indicators]
    R --> S[Update resampled_data]
    S --> Q
    
    K --> T[Check for Signals]
    T --> U{Exit Signal?}
    U -->|Yes| V[Exit Position]
    U -->|No| W{Entry Signal?}
    W -->|Yes| X[Enter Position]
    W -->|No| T
    
    L --> Y[Find ATM Strike]
    Y --> Z[Update Trading Symbols]
    Z --> L
    
    V --> AA[Log Trade]
    X --> AA
    AA --> T
